{"tid":722101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛孟靜稱收到投訴　質疑土瓜灣站一幅牆疑建築廢料建成","createTime":"2018-06-29T08:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T08:09:54.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1919d0f5efbd8d0b7cbe04f2c0b2bea6707b81cc","tid":722101,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:02:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1404304-20180629.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1404304-20180629.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Zp%2FOZbqkgEy4%2Bn%2FMoifyyARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d64da1ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1404304-20180629.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=663a44f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1404304-20180629.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n議會陣線立法會議員毛孟靜表示，收到沙中綫土瓜灣站地盤前工人投訴，二樓月台樓梯的一幅牆懷疑用建築廢料建成，擔心有安全危險。<br />\n<br />\n毛孟靜說，地盤前工人拍攝到往宋皇臺站方向二樓月台的樓梯，有整齊堆積的建築廢料，懷疑是用來建牆。她諮詢資深土木工程師，認為做法百分之百不及格。又說沙中綫前線工程人員對此並不感意外，質疑承建商是為省石屎費用和堆填費用。<br />\n<br />\n毛孟靜擔心相關建築物料會腐爛，造成安全隱憂，促請政府和港鐵盡快交代和解釋相關工程，下周將於立法會提出以特權法調查土瓜灣站的建築問題。"},{"pid":"3e878caf32c6f2792c192afc2a5654582867a4aa","tid":722101,"uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:04:08.000Z","msg":"牙膏"},{"pid":"9907abe597179d029627e6989c4f1d3a5205253d","tid":722101,"uid":147079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:08:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bee6b872148d3f478e68dd788e24d5b96f01b2c","tid":722101,"uid":147079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:08:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c47d163b44776dcc29861a7b659f42920306f47e","tid":722101,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:08:59.000Z","msg":"G持毛EE 繼續爆"},{"pid":"cd747d07ea849e370125e55e348fa99dbe2cc8b5","tid":722101,"uid":20241,